{"tid":960243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廠商會「往工展會」3班跨境車無影　大會：首兩班乘客全於時代廣場落車","createTime":"2018-12-29T08:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T06:32:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26467ce49b3cbc66dbcb02b8b6854033a3d94a57","tid":960243,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181229/s00001/b911e9acca6c339c5e4584970b6f3991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2Fb911e9acca6c339c5e4584970b6f3991.jpg&h=31c2ff16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工展會主辦方香港中華廠商聯合會（廠商會）昨宣布，每天有3班港珠澳大橋跨境巴士服務會在維園天后入口附近增設站點。惟記者今等待近兩小時未見有相關旅遊巴駛過，後獲告知首兩班車的乘客已全在上一站時代廣場下車。<br />\n<br />\n據廠商會所說，由今日起至1月7日，每日會提供3班跨境巴士班次，由珠海口岸前往工展會，分別於早上9時半、10時及10時半出發，車費為130元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n記者今早約10時45分到達天后興發街停車場，惟等待至12時半仍未見有跨境旅遊巴駛入。會方查詢後向記者表示，首兩班車的乘客已全部在時代廣場站下車，無人選到天后維園入口，故未有駛至，而最後一班車的司機則未能聯絡上。<br />\n<br />\n一年一度的工展會已於本月15日開幕，主辦商香港中華廠商聯合會宣布，今天起至工展會閉幕日（2019年1月7日），會每天將提供港珠澳大橋跨境巴士服務，以配合港珠澳大橋通車，及吸引更多內地旅客到工展會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181229/s00001/1546066609638/%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E3%80%91%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8C%E5%BE%80%E5%B7%A5%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D3%E7%8F%AD%E8%B7%A8%E5%A2%83%E8%BB%8A%E7%84%A1%E5%BD%B1-%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-%E9%A6%96%E5%85%A9%E7%8F%AD%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%A8%E6%96%BC%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E8%90%BD%E8%BB%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2F1546066609638%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25BE%2580%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%258D3%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BD%25B1-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%258F%25AD%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%2590%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A&d=K8PvC2QKr1Z73RSyGz68H5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=366d5737\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2F1546066609638%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25BE%2580%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%258D3%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BD%25B1-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%258F%25AD%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%2590%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A&h=60e010e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181229/s00001/1546066609638/%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E3%80%91%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8C%E5%BE%80%E5%B7%A5%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D3%E7%8F%AD%E8%B7%A8%E5%A2%83%E8%BB%8A%E7%84%A1%E5%BD%B1-%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-%E9%A6%96%E5%85%A9%E7%8F%AD%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%A8%E6%96%BC%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E8%90%BD%E8%BB%8A</a>"},{"pid":"28ef257392404da25ccfc28584f46174f8c35e9e","tid":960243,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:59:48.000Z","msg":"口裡說不&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"29f268883f5553dde5b9ca0d8b4d82ed8147c01a","tid":960243,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"而最後一班車的司機則未能聯絡上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5667474ac71701e0facf150e86d9a0fc283b30dd","tid":9